# Library Tooling Family Rules

- Apply this rule when `projectFamily` is `library-tooling`.
- Keep the public surface small and intentional.
- Separate reusable library behavior from repo-local build or automation scripts.
- Require at least one sample invocation, usage example, or packaging smoke step in docs.
